description:
Example usage: put "{SPLIT}" before "{PICKCHARS}" in the keystroke sequence.
Useful when the login screen consists of two parts and it is not known in advance what characters will be needed.

[Announcement](https://sourceforge.net/p/keepass/discussion/329220/thread/1a49bc97c2/)
summary: KeePass plugin that splits auto-typing into distinct parts
author: Krzysztof Łaputa
